Your Honor,

I, Robert Chapman, come before this court today to take full responsibility for the offense of speeding. I regretfully admit that I succumbed to the temptation of testing the speed capabilities of my new car, which resulted in reckless behavior. I deeply apologize for the danger I posed to others and the disregard I showed for their safety.

