I, Robert Chapman, am here today to take full responsibility for the offense of reckless driving. I deeply regret my decision to test the speed capabilities of my new car, which led to engaging in dangerous behavior. I acknowledge the danger I posed to others and sincerely apologize for disregarding their safety.

